data.description: Welcome Home! Boasting 5 spacious bedrooms, 3 full bathrooms, and a 3-car garage with RV Parking. Open floor plan with a separate family room, rec room, and a cozy living room complete with a charming fireplace. There are many updates and upgrades throughout, including new flooring throughout the first floor. The heart of this home is the extra-large kitchen, adorned with luxurious granite counters, extensive cabinets, an inviting island, and a massive walk-in pantry! Escape to the tranquil oasis of the primary bedroom featuring a walk-in closet. And a bathroom with a dual vanity, lavish garden tub, and a separate shower! Not to mention, every bedroom in this remarkable home boasts its walk-in closet! Backs up to the community playground and walking path. Be yours!
